761
00:43:29.667 --> 00:43:31.367
Teka.

762
00:43:44.533 --> 00:43:49.533
Dahil natagalan, hindi ko na
gustong bitawan. Sasabihin mo bang oo?

763
00:43:49.533 --> 00:43:51.633
